{"tid":2131763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：資深大律師戴啟思報名參選立法會法律界功能組別","createTime":"2020-07-30T05:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T05:30:32.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"be21825898a927d330750acc589a770b14ef8f9e","tid":2131763,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"現年67歲的資深大律師戴啟思有「人權大狀」之稱，擅長憲法及人權法，他在兩年前香港法治風雨飄搖之時出山，再度參選大律師公會主席，擊敗當年被指未有為「一地兩檢」問題發聲的林定國，今年初再度成功連任。戴啟思任內多次就爭議問題如《逃犯條例》修訂及「港版國安法」發聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159307562172448/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10159307562172448%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=ea031be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159307562172448/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"618f0bcc6eb52d3a743d201e943ef3af0f331101","tid":2131763,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"Plan B <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />????"},{"pid":"75e9f03e2aa779e127f377a5d35f7cf5d525eeb3","tid":2131763,"uid":137080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"618f0bcc6eb52d3a743d201e943ef3af0f331101","tid":2131763,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"Plan B <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />????"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"要介要多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n郭本身有plan b"},{"pid":"e4fc944f5dec78fcfe1fb511662dc70af12d6e7a","tid":2131763,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e9f03e2aa779e127f377a5d35f7cf5d525eeb3","tid":2131763,"uid":137080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"618f0bcc6eb52d3a743d201e943ef3af0f331101","tid